  {quote: "quotes_2on Debbie: \"It says here you were the C.E.O. of Snaptime Industries.  Care to elaborate on that?\"Larry: \"Sure.  Well, that was the umbrella corporation for my invention, the Snapper.  You know, you snap, lights come on.  Snap, they come off.\"Debbie: \"Uh, uh, uh, didn't they already make that?  (She claps)\"Larry: \"No, no.  That's the Clapper which obviously, stole a bit of our thunder.  Personally, I don't really see what the big difference is.  I mean-- (He claps and snaps)  You know, whatever.  But, um, apparently there is a significant portion of the population that has trouble actually snapping.\"Debbie: \"Clapping's easier.\"Larry: \"Debatable.\"~ ~\n", audio_path: "/Users/mendelblesofsky/Development/projects/Guess-the-Movie/app/assets/audios/Night_At_The_Museum/2.mp3", movie_id: 228},
