  {quote: "quotes_1on Nick Beam (Tim Robbins): \"What is that?\"Zach (Ned Gill): \"Zippy.\"Nick: \"What is Zippy?\"Zach: \"He's a cookie man.\"Nick: \"He's a cookie man...  What is a on the ground behind him?\"Zach: \"That's a trail of chocolate chips.  See where ever Zippy goes, he leaves this magical trail of chocolate for all the boys and girls...\"Nick: \"Magical!  This looks like poop!  It looks like piles of poop.  It looks like zippy's walking along just crapping all over the place.  It looks like he's...\"Zach: \"No, those are chocolate chips.\"Nick: \"And what do you think it looks like?\"Emma (Lisa Mende)?: \"Excriment.\"Nick: \"Zach, let's just say you're about to take a big bite of a cookie.  What's the last thing you want floating around your head?.\"Zach: \"Excriment.\"Nick: \"Excriment right.  Listen, I'm gonna go out on a limb here.  I'm gonna say maybe we should avoid all baul related itmes with this particular product.  Just a hunch you know?\"~ ~\n", audio_path: "/Users/mendelblesofsky/Development/projects/Guess-the-Movie/app/assets/audios/Nothing_To_Lose/1.mp3", movie_id: 231},
